{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"body":"UX design mockup (approved) for the ticket audit-trail page: https://claude.ai/code/artifact/611dac3e-3256-472d-ac4c-03357154b96a\n\nInteractive, self-contained reference implementation of the finalized finding-centric design — sticky gate-status strip, fixed section order, per-round convergence bars, finding-centric four-pass provenance, the neutral threshold meter, criterion-centric completion panel, and empty states. Sample data is illustrative. This is the visual target for story G (depressant-amethyst-wasp)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784070394724280001,"uuid":"6edaeb70-568c-4bec-9636-73a1da98d03f"}